===Etymology===
[[Blend]] of '''[[wiki]]''' and '''[[dictionary]]'''
[[Category:Portmanteaus|wiktionary]]

===Proper noun===
[[Category:English proper nouns]]
{{en-noun-reg-y|Wiktionar|y}}

# A [[collaborative]] project run by the [[w:Wikimedia Foundation|Wikimedia Foundation]] to produce a [[free]] and [[complete]] [[dictionary]] ([[lexicon]] and [[thesaurus]] therein) in every [[language]].
# The dictionary resulting from this project.

